object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT Risk.RiskId as RiskId, 
Risk.PolicyKey as PolicyKey, 
Risk.RiskSystemId as RiskSystemId 
FROM dbo.Risk 
JOIN dbo.claimsummarystats_stg cs 
ON Risk.RiskSystemId = cs.policyref 
where RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'

Risk.BulidingNumber as BulidingNumber

fields.name: v_Indemnity
fields.expression:
IIF (ReserveCd = 'Indemnity' AND (ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Payment' OR 
ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Stop Payment' OR ClaimantTransactionCd = 'Void Payment') , MTDPaidAmt ,null)

fields.name: o_IndemnityTier
fields.expression:
DECODE(TRUE,to_integer(v_Indemnity)=0,'$0',
v_Indemnity>= 1 AND v_Indemnity< 5000 ,'$1-$5k',
v_Indemnity>= 5000 AND v_Indemnity< 10000 , '$5k-$10k',
v_Indemnity>= 10000 AND v_Indemnity< 250000 , '$10k-$25k',
v_Indemnity>= 25000 AND v_Indemnity< 50000 , '$25k-$50k',
v_Indemnity>= 50000 AND v_Indemnity< 75000 , '$50k-$75k',
v_Indemnity>= 75000 AND v_Indemnity< 100000 ,'$75k-$100k',
v_Indemnity>= 100000 , '$100k+',null)
